data.description: Welcome to 3150 E 3300 N! This spacious 3 bed, 2 bath house with a family room is a gem. It offers 2,126 sqft of living space, new exterior/interior paint, and ductless mini splits for A/C and heating. And the best part? It's situated on a generous 4.68-acre lot, perfect for all your outdoor projects and even keeping livestock or horses. With 5 water shares, you can ensure the land stays lush and green. If you're interested, give your favorite realtor a call to schedule a tour of this one-of-a-kind property.
